# Plan: Fix Icon Cards Layout - Icon Left, Text Right

> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.

**Goal:** Change icon cards from vertical stack (icon above text) to horizontal layout (icon left, text right) with vertical dashed line connecting through icon centers.

**Architecture:** CSS-only changes to restructure the icon card layout.

**Tech Stack:** Astro, CSS

---

## Analysis

**Current layout:**
- Icon on top, centered
- Title and description below, right-aligned
- Dashed line on the right side

**Target layout:**
- Icon on LEFT side of card
- Title and description on RIGHT side of icon
- Text LEFT-aligned
- Dashed vertical line runs through CENTER of icons (connecting them)

---

## Implementation Tasks

### Task 1: Restructure icon card to horizontal layout

**File:** `src/pages/greenblocks.astro`

**Find (around line 1090-1150):**
```css
/* Icon Cards (Problem section) - vertical stack with connecting lines */
.gb-problem-cards {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  position: relative;
}

.gb-icon-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-end;
  text-align: right;
  padding: 1rem 0;
  position: relative;
}

/* Dashed connecting line between cards */
.gb-icon-card:not(:last-child)::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  right: 40px;
  top: calc(100% - 1rem);
  width: 1px;
  height: 2rem;
  border-left: 2px dashed rgba(180, 165, 140, 0.5);
}

.gb-icon-card-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: rgba(235, 228, 216, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(180, 165, 140, 0.4);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(120, 100, 80, 0.7);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.gb-icon-card-icon :global(svg) {
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}

.gb-icon-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--gb-font-display);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gb-text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.gb-icon-card p {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--gb-text-muted);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 200px;
}
```

**Replace with:**
```css
/* Icon Cards (Problem section) - horizontal layout with connecting line */
.gb-problem-cards {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 40px;
}

/* Vertical dashed line connecting all icons */
.gb-problem-cards::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 40px;
  top: 40px;
  bottom: 40px;
  width: 0;
  border-left: 2px dashed rgba(180, 165, 140, 0.5);
}

.gb-icon-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  position: relative;
}

.gb-icon-card-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  min-width: 80px;
  background: rgba(235, 228, 216, 0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(180, 165, 140, 0.4);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(120, 100, 80, 0.7);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.gb-icon-card-icon :global(svg) {
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}

.gb-icon-card-text {
  padding-top: 0.5rem;
}

.gb-icon-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--gb-font-display);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gb-text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.gb-icon-card p {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--gb-text-muted);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 220px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
```

